text: Skive IK is a Danish football club currently playing in the Danish 1st Division. They play at Skive Stadium in Skive in Jutland, which has a capacity of 10,000. == Current squad == Updated by 17 October 2020 == Staff == {| |valign="top"| * Coach: Thomas Røll * Ass.Coach: Martin Thomsen |width="50"| |valign="top"| * GK trainer: Morten Jannichen * Physio: Henrik Nissen |width="50"| |valign="top"| * Team coordinator: Lars Lunne |width="50"| |} == External links == * Official site Category:Football clubs in Denmark Category:Skive Municipality Category:Association football clubs established in 1901 Category:1901 establishments in Denmark
